i had such a good time in london this week etcetc
got back last night and my GOD do i hate my family

im basically stuck in my room because if i go downstairs im just going to get more crap off them. my mum came into my room this morning saying shed been talking to my cousin and accusing me of a bunch of stuff. they think theyre so sneaky the way they are piecing loads of random stuff together and talking about me behind my back. i can just imagine them staging an intervention any day now. HOW o.c.


just go aaawwwwwwwwwwaaaaaaayyyyy

so i went to look for a job. i applied in a ton of places and hopefully somewhere will be nice and hire me.

i really need to go to london to get some clothes before bhasvic because im quite bored of the clothes they have in the shops here as you just KNOW everyones going to have them.

im going to be so BUSYYY and i dont know whether its a good or a bad thing. theres a party and then a wedding this weekend and i sure hope its fun! im really not looking forward to next week because its going to be so tiring and blahblahblah but hopefully worth it in the end.

some people are being SO annoying and its making me never ever want to speak to them again except im going to have to. i wish theyd just SHUT UPPPPPPPP!

history - A*
english - A*

drama - A

double science B/B

imso happy!
especially my A in latin because i thought id failed. id like to rub it in mr williamssss face!

today i came home from celebrating etc and found a nice note from my mum and a pile of mingles? i dont know why someone would leave me a pile of mingles but it was really nice and just what i wanted....!
going out tonight should be a barrel of laughs!

hope everyone else did themselves PROUD

OFF
